    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>关于Markdown</h3>

<p>Markdown是一种to HTML的语言，就如同coffeescript to javascript、less to css一样。
当然这种语言存在必然有其存在的意义，否然直接写html好了啦。
Markdown官方解释是其用途是：<strong>用來作為一種網路內容的寫作用語言</strong>。
写作更多的是处理文字的排版等，那么直接用HTML去写确实大材小用，Markdown便可用来方便编写以及提升源文件的可阅读性。</p>

<h3>语法:</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>HTML 语法</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>首先，Markdown是支持直接写HTML的，就如同在less文件中也可以直接写css。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;div style="width:200px;height:80px;background-color:green;">&lt;/div>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>testbbb&amp;>&lt; (看，&lt;code>&lt;、&gt;、&amp;&lt;/code>等不需要转义使用了哦~)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<div style="width:200px;height:80px;background-color:green;"></div>


<p>testbbb&amp;>&lt; (看，<code>&lt;、&gt;、&amp;</code>等不需要转义使用了哦~)</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>段落和換行</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>Markdown中一个以上的空行会分隔出段落，下面fisrtP会在一个段落里，但是我们会发现中间有个空格。
那是因为浏览器会把p标签内的文本换行转化为一个空格。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'>firstPfirstPfirstPfirstPfirstPfirstPfirstP
</span><span class='line'>firstPfirstPfirstP<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>secondPsecondPsecondP
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>firstPfirstPfirstPfirstPfirstPfirstPfirstP
firstPfirstPfirstP</p>

<p>secondPsecondPsecondP</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>标题</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>很容易理解，这里只列出最简单的一种写法。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;h1&gt;</span>This is an H1<span class="nt">&lt;/h1&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;h3&gt;</span>This is an H3<span class="nt">&lt;/h3&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;h6&gt;</span>This is an H6<span class="nt">&lt;/h6&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h1>This is an H1</h1>

<h3>This is an H3</h3>

<h6>This is an H6</h6>

<ul>
<li><strong>引言</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>就是像回复邮件中引用的那种情形。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;</span>This is the first level of quoting.<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;h6&gt;</span>This is nested blockquote.<span class="nt">&lt;/h6&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p></blockquote>

<p>This is the first level of quoting.</p>

<blockquote><h6>This is nested blockquote.</h6></blockquote></blockquote>

<ul>
<li><strong>列表</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>有序列表的数值改动是无用的，而且貌似只能从1开始。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'>1.  Bird
</span><span class='line'>2.  McHale
</span><span class='line'>3.  Parish<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;</span>*   Red
</span><span class='line'>*   Green
</span><span class='line'>*   Blue
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<pre><code>1.  Bird
2.  McHale
3.  Parish
    *   Red
    *   Green
    *   Blue
</code></pre>

<ul>
<li><strong>代码块</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>4个空格或一个tab缩进即代表代码块，这里只是处理成了pre元素，octopress提供了更好的代码展示插件。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'>This is a normal paragraph:<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;</span>This is a code block.
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>This is a normal paragraph:</p>

<pre><code>This is a code block.
</code></pre>

<ul>
<li><strong>分割线</strong></li>
</ul>


<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;hr</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<hr />

<ul>
<li><strong>链接</strong></li>
</ul>


<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'>This is <span class="nt">&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">&quot;http://example.com/&quot;</span> <span class="na">title=</span><span class="s">&quot;Title&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>an example<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;</span> inline link.
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>This is <a href="http://example.com/" title="Title">an example</a> inline link.</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>文字修饰</strong></li>
</ul>


<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;em&gt;</span>single asterisks<span class="nt">&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;</span>double asterisks<span class="nt">&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;</span>printf()<span class="nt">&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>A backtick-delimited string in a code span: <span class="nt">&lt;code&gt;</span>`foo`<span class="nt">&lt;/code&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p><em>single asterisks</em></p>

<p><strong>double asterisks</strong></p>

<p><code>printf()</code></p>

<p>A backtick-delimited string in a code span: <code>`foo`</code></p>

<ul>
<li><strong>图片</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>octopress也提供了更好的图片插件。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;img</span> <span class="na">src=</span><span class="s">&quot;/images/logo.png&quot;</span> <span class="na">title=</span><span class="s">&quot;Optional title&quot;</span> <span class="na">alt=</span><span class="s">&quot;Alt text&quot;</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p><img src="/images/logo.png" title="Optional title" alt="Alt text" /></p>

<ul>
<li><strong>转义字符</strong></li>
</ul>


<p>用反斜杠来转义。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
<span class='line-number'>18</span>
<span class='line-number'>19</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>*literal asterisks*<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>\   反斜線
</span><span class='line'>`   反引號
</span><span class='line'>*   星號
</span><span class='line'>_   底線
</span><span class='line'>{}  大括號
</span><span class='line'>[]  方括號
</span><span class='line'>()  括號<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;h1&gt;</span>井字號<span class="nt">&lt;/h1&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;ul&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;</span>加號<span class="nt">&lt;/li&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;</span>減號
</span><span class='line'>.   英文句點
</span><span class='line'>!   驚嘆號
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></li>
</ul>


<p>*literal asterisks*</p>

<hr />

<br/>


<br/>


<p>上面是对markdown最常用，最简单的一些语法进行了介绍，后面还会介绍下octopress编写方面的一些插件。</p>

<p>参考资料：<a href="http://markdown.tw/">http://markdown.tw/</a></p>
